<pb facs="#facs_141" id="69v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r1l1">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> nach <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Rum<ex>m</ex>el</expan> geſandt / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> vnd <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r1l2"><expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſo ıſt er auf dıſʒ ʒeıt nıht anheim geweſen . wenn er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r1l3"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt / <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır denn daran gemant ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r1l4">Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> reden vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſuchen</expan> Ob er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht on recht becʒaln welle . / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r1l5">möcht des nıht geſein ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> knecht oder <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
