</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Cönczlin Übelfeils,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> knechts, und <expan>C<ex>las</ex></expan>
<expan>Rum<ex>m</ex>els</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <pb facs="#facs_141" id="69v"/>wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        nach <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Rum<ex>m</ex>el</expan> gesandt und <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        mit im <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        So ist er auf disz zeit niht anheim gewesen; wenn er
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt,
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wir denn daran gemant, so
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit
                        im <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> reden und
                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan>, ob er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht
                        on recht beczaln welle; möcht des niht gesein, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> knecht oder <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von <add>dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>las</ex></expan>
<expan>Rum<ex>m</ex>el</expan> bey uns anheim ist, on geverd. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
